1. *Dece* su još uvek mala da razumeju šta se dešava. (The children are still too young to understand what is happening.)
2. Ona će i dalje biti tu da podrži svoju *decu*. (She will still be here to support her children.)
3. Očekuje se da roditelji obezbede najbolje uslove za svoju *decu*. (It is expected that parents provide the best conditions for their children.)
4. Oni imaju troje *djece*. (They have three children.)
5. Ona se brine o svojoj *deci* od ranog uzrasta. (She has been taking care of her children since early age.)